## Testing Edge Cases

```ruby
test "handles empty body gracefully" do
  article = Article.new(body: "")
  assert_equal 0, article.reading_time
end

test "handles nil values" do
  article = Article.new(title: nil, body: nil)
  assert_not article.valid?
end

test "handles very long text" do
  article = Article.new(body: "a" * 1_000_000)
  assert article.reading_time > 0
end
```

